# Draft:The Black Labyrinth / A Requiem For the Goblin King

The Black Labyrinth / A Requiem For the Goblin King is the 13th studio album by Cuban American dark cabaret singer Voltaire, released in 2022.
Track listing
Personnel
* Voltaire — vocals
* Mike Garson — piano
* Gail Ann Dorsey —  bass
* Sterling Campbell — drums
* Earl Slick — guitars
* Ray Toro — guitars
* Mark Plati — producer
* Mia Asano — violin
* Ally Crowley-Duncan — bagpipes
